Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.36,0:00:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕 對不起 今天我也
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.05,0:00:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.49,0:01:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕 有感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕的在我裡面不停地抽動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕 好熱 熱勁往上湧 身體變得好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好深 要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.51,0:05:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.94,0:05:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 已經
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.27,0:05:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕的大大的 爽 爽 裕 爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感情 竟如此熾烈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:27.15,Maho,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心情和她的心情交織起來 所以才會如此強烈反應
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:31.09,Maho,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不說一直寵著她 就因為這樣的你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:37.68,Maho,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一意孤行下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:39.58,Maho,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你和她可都不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.55,0:06:55.98,Reunion,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和平時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽曬屁股了 再不起遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 理英
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 等等 綾香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 這時候來我家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是有點在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那恩愛的男朋友現在還在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 討厭 剛才 就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就真讓你這麼著迷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我 已經按耐不住這份感情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對得不到幸福的啊 這只會讓你們兩個都受傷的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 這回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別蒙我了 看看現在的你我越發肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.83,0:07:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還在這個城市裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管你這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理英
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是現實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒天下之大不韙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到深處 好深 來 深處 一直插到深處
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想一直和你這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.82,0:10:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡你了 愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只喜歡你一個 喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 這個時間把你叫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還得讓你翹課
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能幹這種壞事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是穿泳衣會好點？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的 我要穿上估計像個老太婆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:50.55,Reunion,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？ 摩穗同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:09.00,Maho,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感情氾濫得太嚴重了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.42,0:13:14.51,Maho,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不結束這段孽緣的話 就會失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼自私 為裕著想一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:30.69,Reunion,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是讓她發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:37.08,Reunion,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為裕著想一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\frz12\pos(335,250)\3c&HFFC485&\blur2}等著你···。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:50.19,Reunion,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.30,0:13:55.32,Reunion,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明如此喜歡 卻如此撕心裂肺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:58.04,Reunion,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對得不到幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:01.10,Reunion,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕治同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師？ 桐崎老師 您沒受傷吧 老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來…了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕 對不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情只有裕才
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到深處 爽 爽 爽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來 繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 爽 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩穗在這裡 一直一直都在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使多麼傷心 摩穗都一直在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.78,0:17:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 已經可以去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.53,0:18:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.82,0:18:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你呢 來這裡可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想你的立場 還有理英的立場
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉 但是請你必須回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的感情無法控制了 明天你就會明白了 包括她的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 早上好 您沒事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我已經好了 偶感小恙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉害大家這麼擔心 要上課了 快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 東野君你也快去上課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師身體好些了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好多了 不必再擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:46.43,Maho,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她用情太深了 對你的事已經
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:53.63,Maho,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太強烈的感情讓她痛苦 於是只能在這裡讓她解脫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.85,0:20:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 知道是這樣的話 從一開始就應該
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明這麼喜愛著裕 卻什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.24,0:20:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩穗好沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.54,0:23:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.12,0:23:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.22,0:23:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.71,0:23:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.56,0:23:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.03,0:23:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.63,0:23:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.39,0:25:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 摩穗對不起你 變成這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.52,0:25:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩穗其實
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.22,0:25:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.26,0:25:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.33,0:25:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身子沒事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.75,0:25:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了 綾香太過擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.53,0:25:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.86,0:25:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕的話要不我們去喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.68,0:26:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病剛剛好 別胡鬧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.83,0:26:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總感覺輕鬆了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.84,0:26:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是因為在病院裡面睡多了？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.43,0:26:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.61,0:26:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 感覺有一股熟悉的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.60,0:26:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 走吧
